<li class="toclevel-2"><a href="#Controversial_movements"><span class="tocnumber">3.4</span> <span class="toctext">Controversial movements</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-3"><a href="#Pre-Reformation"><span class="tocnumber">3.4.1</span> <span class="toctext">Pre-Reformation</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-3"><a href="#Post-Reformation"><span class="tocnumber">3.4.2</span> <span class="toctext">Post-Reformation</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-3"><a href="#Contemporary_Theological_movements"><span class="tocnumber">3.4.3</span> <span class="toctext">Contemporary Theological movements</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-1"><a href="#Notes"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">Notes</span></a></li>
