<li id="cite_note-Brecht12-9"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Brecht12_9-0" title="">^</a></b> Brecht, Martin. <i>Martin Luther</i>. tr. James L. Schaaf, Philadelphia: Fortress Press, 1985–93, 1:12-27.</li>
<li id="cite_note-Wriedt-10"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Wriedt_10-0" title="">^</a></b> Wriedt, Markus. "Luther's Theology," in <i>The Cambridge Companion to Luther</i>. New York: Cambridge University Press, 2003, 88–94.</li>
